00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:14.160
va ularni bir-biriga solishtiring.

00:00:14.160 --> 00:00:17.550
Biz buni SUM yordamida bajaramiz,

00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:19.439
u xuddi COUNT kabi ishlaydi.

00:00:19.439 --> 00:00:21.420
