00:00:21.420 --> 00:00:24.930
* dan foydalanishdan ko‘ra. Standart

00:00:24.930 --> 00:00:26.460
ikkala nostandartdan ham mashhur ko‘rinadi.

00:00:26.460 --> 00:00:31.080
